MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1032102106062760309}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a45ffc7ebd05a6849a9ced81e0140741, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  nameDisplay: {fileID: 0}
  dialogueDisplay: {fileID: 0}
  nextArrow: {fileID: 0}
  dialoguePanel: {fileID: 0}
  uiFader: {fileID: 0}
  mingleTracker: {fileID: 0}
  typingSpeed: 0.0333
  dialogueLines:
  - characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: "The invitation promised a \"Gala of the Century.\" The reality is
      six people in a drafty rotunda that smells like lemon polish and desperation.
      We were the only ones who actually showed up, and I was starting to suspect
      the others that were invited just smarter than us.\r"
    isItalic: 1
  - characterName: 'MAXIMILIAN MIDAS '
    sentence: 'Friends. You were chosen tonight because you are the select few, the
      only few, qualified to witness my brilliance.

'
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: 'MAXIMILIAN MIDAS '
    sentence: Out of every scholar and socialite I invited, only those with the most...
      invested interests showed up.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: 'JULIAN VANE '
    sentence: "Max, please. If I wanted to be insulted in an empty room, I\u2019d
      go to my own gallery openings. Can we skip to the good part?"
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: 'MAXIMILIAN MIDAS '
    sentence: "Then you\u2019ll be waiting a long time, Julian. As I was saying\u2014"
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: 'PENNY STERLING  '
    sentence: "Sir, the guests haven\u2019t, I mean looking at the door, I don't
      think anyone else is coming. The parking lot is a graveyard."
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: 'MAXIMILIAN MIDAS  '
    sentence: "You are paid to stand there and be silent, Penny! If I wanted commentary
      from the staff, I\u2019d talk to the gargoyles on the roof. Now, the Aurelian
      Institute represents the height of\u2014"
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DR. HARLOW
    sentence: "I am here because you insisted this was urgent. You\u2019ve kept your
      staff working extended hours all week."
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DR. HARLOW
    sentence: "So I\u2019ll ask plainly. What exactly are you unveiling?"
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: MAXIMILIAN MIDAS
    sentence: I am trying to unveil a masterpiece! Iris, are you getting all of this?
      I want my brilliance captured from every angle.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: 'IRIS GABLE '
    sentence: "I\u2019m getting it, Max. Though if you want 'brilliance,' you might
      want to stop scowling. It ruins the composition."
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: 'IRIS GABLE '
    sentence: "Or you could just tell us what\u2019s under the sheet."
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: 'MAXIMILIAN MIDAS  '
    sentence: Fine! Witness the future of my legacy. I call it...
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: 'MAXIMILIAN MIDAS  '
    sentence: The Midas Grand University.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: "A university. He dragged us all here, on a Tuesday night, in the rain,
      to look at a blueprint in a hollowed out museum. I've seen more exciting things
      under police tape.\r"
    isItalic: 1
  - characterName: 'JULIAN VANE '
    sentence: You're serious. You are actually serious right now?
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: 'DR. HARLOW '
    sentence: Do you have any idea how long it takes to properly transfer a collection
      of this size? The documentation alone would take years! You've been clearing
      the halls because you'd already planned to gut the place!
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: 'MAXIMILIAN MIDAS '
    sentence: It will be absorbed into the university. Along with the collection.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: 'MAXIMILIAN MIDAS '
    sentence: You are all being left behind. That's rather your business.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: 'IRIS GABLE '
    sentence: Wow. Okay.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: 'PENNY STERLING '
    sentence: "Max, you can't just\u2014"
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: MAXIMILIAN MIDAS
    sentence: The bar is open. Take one last look around while you still can. I have
      calls to make!
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: 
    sentence: "And like that, Max walks away.\r"
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: "Everyone in this room just got some kind of bad news. And now we're
      all supposed to have a nice time together. Great party, Max.\r"
    isItalic: 1
